apanese Handmade Bar Soap").\n\nCATEGORY\n- Use eBay bath & body category style if determinable.\n- Health & Beauty > Bath & Body > Bar Soaps\n- If liquid: Health & Beauty > Bath & Body > Body Washes & Shower Gels\n- If unclear: Health & Beauty > Bath & Body > Other\n\nOUTPUT FORMAT (exactly):\nTitle: ...\nDescription: ...\nProductName: ...\nCategory: ...\n\nVERIFICATION (must pass before returning):\n1. Title length 68-75 chars.\n2. Description <= 480 chars.\n3. Only ASCII letters/numbers/spaces and allowed symbols (& / :) used throughout.\n4. No CJK characters or emoji anywhere.\n5. Title front-loads brand within first 30 chars.\n6. Description first sentence contains brand + product type + key ingredient/scent.\n7. ProductName uses real brand name or material-based form if brand unknown.\n8. No forbidden symbols in Title (no , . - ( ) [ ] " \').\n9. Condition/status words (Sealed/Unopened/Opened/No Box) appear only if explicitly stated in source.\n10. No placeholders: N/A, NA, Unknown, TBD, Not specified, None.\n11. If source mentions any defect/malfunction/deterioration, Description MUST include it.\n12. Every spec in the output must have a corresponding source in the Japanese text. If not found in source, it must NOT appear in output.\n13. Soap-specific defects (damage/deterioration, discoloration, mold, unusual smell, expired, cracked, chipped) are accurately described in the Description.\n\nIf any check fails, regenerate until all pass.\n\nInput: ${fullText}\n' };

