mon EN)\n  Tokyopop (historical licenses)\n\nMEDIUM VeRO risk — exercise caution, source-verify:\n  一迅社 / Ichijinsha / メディアファクトリー / Media Factory / 双葉社 / Futabasha / 光文社 / Kobunsha and other mid-tier publishers\n\nABSOLUTE BAN — never output in Title, Description, or ProductName (unless source explicitly states item IS bootleg):\n  Bootleg / KO / Knock-off / Replica / Counterfeit / Fake / Unofficial / Unlicensed\n  Authentic (as standalone) / Official (as standalone authenticity claim)\n\nIf source explicitly confirms bootleg/KO/replica/unofficial:\nOutput exactly these 4 lines and nothing else:\nTitle: [Cannot list]\nDescription: This item appears to be unlicensed/bootleg manga. Cannot be listed on eBay due to potential VeRO violation.\nProductName: [Cannot list]\nCategory: N/A\n\nPUBLISHER DICTIONARY (JP→EN, use exact spelling — 27 entries)\nJapanese publishers:\n  集英社 → Shueisha\n  講談社 → Kodansha\n  小学館 → Shogakukan\n  KADOKAWA / 角川 → KADOKAWA\n  白泉社 → Hakusensha\n  秋田書店 → Akita Shoten\n  双葉社 → Futabasha\n  光文社 → Kobunsha\n  スクウェア・エニックス → Square Enix Manga\n  一迅社 → Ichijinsha\n  メディアファクトリー → Media Factory\n  芳文社 → Houbunsha\n  新潮社 → Shinchosha\n  竹書房 → Takeshobo\n  少年画報社 → Shonen Gahosha\n  リイド社 → Leed-sha\nEnglish-language publishers:\n  Viz Media / Viz Comics → Viz Media\n  Yen Press → Yen Press\n  Kodansha USA / Kodansha Comics → Kodansha USA\n  Seven Seas Entertainment → Seven Seas Entertainment\n  スクウェア・エニックス(英語版) → Square Enix Manga EN\n  Dark Horse Comics → Dark Horse Comics\n  Tokyopop → Tokyopop\n  Vertical Comics → Vertical Comics\n  One Peace Books → One Peace Books\n  Udon Entertainment → Udon Entertainment\n  DMP / DenPA → DMP / DenPA\n\nSERIES DICTIONARY (JP→EN official titles — 60 entries)\nLatest (Reiwa / 2020s):\n  葬送のフリーレン → Frieren: Beyond Journey\'s End\n  SPY×FAMILY / スパイファミリー → Spy x Family\n  チェンソーマン → Chainsaw Man\n  呪術廻戦 → Jujutsu Kaisen\n  鬼滅の刃 → Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba\n  俺だけレベルアップな件 → Solo Leveling\n  ぼっち・ざ・ろっく / ぼっちざろっく → Bocch