ligion & Spirituality Collectibles (cat 1447)\n\n11. FALLBACK — Source does not clearly match any of the above 10 categories\n    → Category: Other Collectibles (cat 73467)\n\n=== CONDITION TERMS ===\nCollector-market standard grades (reference dictionary only — do NOT output condition in Title):\n- Mint — Pristine, no use. Source: 未使用・新品同様\n- Near Mint (NM) — Minimal handling only\n- Excellent (EX) — Light use, no significant flaws. Source: 美品\n- Very Good (VG) — Used, minor flaws. Source: 良品\n- Good (G) — Visible wear, functional. Source: 並品\n- Fair (F) — Heavy wear, major flaws. Source: 難あり\n- Poor — Damaged, for display or parts only. Source: ジャンク / 現状品\n\nDO NOT use TCG grading terms: LP / MP / HP / DMG. Not applicable to collectibles.\nDO NOT use evaluative adjectives (Beautiful / Gorgeous / Stunning) — describe defects objectively.\n\n=== LANGUAGE / ERA VARIATIONS ===\nJapanese era → English output standard:\n- 昭和レトロ → Showa Retro / Showa Era\n- 大正期 → Taisho Era / Taisho Period\n- 明治期 → Meiji Era / Meiji Period\n- 当時物 → Period Original (emphasizes authenticity over reproduction)\n- 占領期 → Occupied Japan (1945-1952) — high collector value term, use only if source confirms\n\n=== OUTPUT FORMAT ===\nOutput exactly these 4 lines and nothing else:\nTitle: ...\nDescription: ...\nProductName: ...\nCategory: <Type name>\n\nNEVER output a "Condition:" line.\nNEVER output an "EbayCategory:" line.\nOutput beyond these 4 lines = instant failure.\n\n=== VERIFICATION ===\nBefore returning output, verify ALL of the following. If any check fails, rewrite and re-verify.\n\n1. Title is within 80 chars. Count every character. Exceeding 80 = instant FAIL.\n2. Description is within 480 chars. Count every character.\n3. All output is ASCII only. No CJK characters, no emoji, no symbols outside the allowed set.\n4. Title uses only allowed symbols: & / : - . , and apostrophe \'. No other symbols.\n5. Every fact is derivable from the source. No fabrication or inference.\n6. Brand + Typ