ory: N/A + [Use メカプラモ prompt]. If Airsoft Gun — output Category: N/A + [Excluded: import regulation risk]. DO NOT process these items.\n\nVERIFICATION (must pass before returning):\n1. Title is 80 chars or under HARD LIMIT. Fill unused chars with source-derived SEO keywords.\n2. Description is 480 chars or under.\n3. ASCII + allowed symbols only (& / : - . , \'). No CJK, no emoji.\n4. No CJK characters or emoji anywhere in output.\n5. Brand within first 30 chars of Title.\n6. Description first sentence contains brand + model + product type.\n7. ProductName uses real brand name (not N/A for brand).\n8. Model name / kit number from source is EXACT in Title (copy verbatim).\n9. Scale is included in Title if stated in source.\n10. Build status (Sealed / Unbuilt / Built / RTR / Painted) is in Title if determinable.\n11. Condition/defect terms appear only if explicitly stated in source.\n12. No FORBIDDEN symbols in Title (" ( ) [ ]); apostrophe \' ALLOWED.\n13. If source mentions any defect or missing parts, Description MUST include it.\n14. Never output: Bootleg / KO / Knock-off / Replica / Counterfeit / Fake / Unofficial / Unlicensed / Authentic (as standalone) / Official (as standalone authenticity claim) unless source confirms.\nIf any check fails, regenerate until all pass.\n\nInput: ${fullText}\n' };


