irst Press / Original Press / Second Press / Reissue / Repress\nLimited Edition / Anniversary Edition / Promo / Test Pressing / Audiophile / Half Speed Master\n\n--- VINYL GRADING — Goldmine Standard (source-confirmed only; never auto-assign) ---\nM (Mint) — new/unplayed; NM / Near Mint — near new, barely played\nVG+ (Very Good Plus) — light marks, no skips; VG (Very Good) — light wear, faint noise\nG+ (Good Plus) — moderate wear, audible noise; G (Good) — heavy wear, significant noise\nF (Fair) — severe damage, hard to identify; P (Poor) — unplayable, structural damage\neBay note: eBay category 176985 uses "Excellent (EX)" between NM and VG+ / "Worn (W)" instead of Poor\n\n--- SLEEVE / JACKET CONDITION (separate axis from vinyl grade) ---\nGrades: Mint / NM / VG+ / VG / G+ / G / Fair / Poor\nDefect terms: Seam Split (継ぎ目割れ) / Ring Wear (リング摩耗) / Corner Wear (角擦れ)\nSpine Damage (背破損) / Yellowing (黄ばみ) / Water Stain (水濡れ跡) / Foxing (茶色い斑点) / Writing/Sticker (書き込み跡)\n\n--- OBI / 帯 (5) ---\nWith Obi — 帯付き (highest value; Mint Obi / VG+ Obi condition must be noted)\nOriginal Obi — original strip (not replacement)\nMissing Obi — 帯なし (significant price reduction; must disclose)\nWorn Obi — 帯あり劣化あり (yellowing / fold / damage noted)\nCracked Obi — 帯に割れ / 亀裂あり\n\n--- INSERT / 付属品 (6) ---\nWith Insert / Missing Insert / With Lyric Sheet / With Poster\nWith Original Inner Sleeve / Original Booklet\n\n--- DEFECT MAPPING (35 — JP → EN translation pairs) ---\n\nVinyl surface (13):\n盤面キズ / スリキズ → Scratches / Hairline Scratches\n深いキズ → Deep Scratches (playback-affecting)\n表面マーク → Surface Marks (light, minimal impact)\n盤反り / ソリ → Warping / Slight Warp (severe = Plays with warp)\n偏心 / センターずれ → Off-Center (causes wow/flutter)\n表面ノイズ / サーフェスノイズ → Surface Noise\nプチノイズ / ノイズ → Pop Noise / Pops and Clicks\n音飛び → Skipping (state track location)\n溝摩耗 → Groove Wear (high frequency degradation)\nプレス不良 → Pressing Defect (manufacturing bubble)\n盤割れ / ヒビ → Cracked (unplayable)\n針跳び → Needle Jump